ed="T" n="0810a05"/><persName key="A001248">釋景霄</persName>，俗姓<name>徐</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000012388">丹丘</placeName>人也。初之聽涉在<persName key="A011640">表<lb
ed="T" n="0810a06"/><roleName>公</roleName></persName>門，後慕<persName key="A011655">守言<roleName>闍<anchor xml:id="beg0810sgsz1"/>黎<anchor xml:id="end0810sgsz1"/></roleName></persName>義集，敷演于<placeName key="PL000000012388">丹丘</placeName>。執性<lb
ed="T" n="0810a07"/>嚴毅，寡與人交。狷急<ptr type="glossary" target="#g926"/>自持，多事凌轥<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1245"/>，形器<lb
ed="T" n="0810a08"/>惡弱。後納請往<placeName key="PL000000013605"><placeName>金華</placeName><placeName>東白山</placeName></placeName>，獎訓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g927"/>初學。時<lb
ed="T" n="0810a09"/>有<placeName key="PL000000018571">江西</placeName><persName key="A011654">徽猷</persName>律匠，出義記曰《龜鑑錄》，多學<lb
ed="T" n="0810a10"/>彭亨<ptr type="glossary" target="#g539"/>，領徒到<persName key="A001248">霄</persName>寺，正值講次<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1422"/>當〈持犯篇〉<ptr target="#n1882"/>，再<lb
ed="T" n="0810a11"/>三歎賞。自此聲溢價高。每晨滴茶，一旦化<lb
ed="T" n="0810a12"/>為乳焉。著記二十卷，號《簡正》<ptr target="#n1883"/>，言以思擇<lb
ed="T" n="0810a13"/>力故，去邪說而簡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1136"/>取正義也。<persName key="A003552"><persName>武肅王</persName><persName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0810a14"/>召於<placeName key="PL000000012110">臨安</placeName>故鄉，宰任<placeName key="PL000000012103">竹林寺</placeName>。未幾，命赴<placeName key="PL000000009882">北<lb
ed="T" n="0810a15"/>塔寺</placeName>臨壇，<date from-iso="+0927-02-10" key="j20596802060034" to-iso="+0928-01-30"><name>天成</name>二年</date>也。次命住<placeName key="PL000000011485">南真身寶<lb
ed="T" n="0810a16"/>塔寺</placeName>，終焉。遷葬于<placeName key="PL000000012299">大慈山</placeName>塢，以本受師號<lb
ed="T" n="0810a17"/>塔曰<placeName key="PL000000058078">清涼</placeName>是歟。</p>
